.guideline-wrapper#email-signature
  .guideline-section
    .col-sm-12
      :markdown
        ### Email Signature
        This is a branded email signature for #{clientName}.  Click the link below and copy + paste into your email client.  
        Please contact your IT support staff for help with changing the signature on your email client.  Here is a link with 
        instructions for [Outlook](https://support.office.com/en-us/article/Change-an-email-signature-7db4abed-abe1-44aa-b423-38ab143427fa) 
        and a [PDF](./brand-files/email-signature/how-to-add-email-signature.pdf) with instructions for Mac Mail, Gmail, and iOS
  .guideline-section
    .col-sm-5
      h5 Create a personal signature:
        small Add your details below to create a personalized email signature
      form(id='generateEmailSig', action='brand-files/email-signature/email-signature.html', method='GET', target='_blank' )
        input(name='name',type='text',placeholder='Your Name')
        input(name='title',type='text',placeholder='Job Title')
        input(name='phone',type='phone',placeholder='Phone Number')
        input(type='submit',value='Generate Signature')
      a(href='brand-files/email-signature/email-signature.html' target='_blank') View a sample email signature    
    .col-sm-7
      img(src='brand-files/email-signature/email-signature@2x.png', alt='Acceptable Configurations')
